Name: SYNC_BYTE_1
Description: The first byte of every message between the secondary device and the base.

Name: SYNC_BYTE_2
Description: The second byte of every message between the secondary device and the base.

Name: RESET_CHIP_VERIFICATION_CODE
Description: Verification code to reset the chip.

Name: SET_FLIGHT_VERIFICATION_CODE
Description: Verification code to set the flight state.
